        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do I need to be home for pickup and delivery?</summary>
          <p>Someone needs to be available to let the driver in. You don't have to do any lifting — just direct where it goes. Contactless delivery in a lobby or garage is possible with clear instructions.</p>
        </details>
